animeTitle: Yoshida no Matsue Beauty Daisakusen Prologue
animeDescription: A Matsue City collaboration anime with Eagle Talon. Yoshida helps Hifumi Arai discover beauty and skin care within the city after she gives up hope for any long lasting beauty.
